    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_10693-10730",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "10693-10730",
      "markText": "人们论证说，如果一个制度竟允许将妇女当成下等人，那这个制度必然只能产生弱国",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10693&rangeEnd=10730",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10693&rangeEnd=10730"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_14655-14736",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14655-14736",
      "markText": "名妓被带进文字记载，并能成为我当今沉思冥想的对象，只是因为一个世纪以前的男人在渴念与感伤中遥想她们所属的世界，因为他们，还有中国，已经永远地失去了这样的一个世界。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14655&rangeEnd=14736",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14655&rangeEnd=14736"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_700-800",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "700-800",
      "markText": "事实上，只是当有人想对她们进行赞誉、谴责或是统计其人数、进行监管、为她们治病、分析其病理、对世人发出警示、拯救她们、取缔娼妓业或者利用她们作为社会象征等等——只是在这种种情形下，娼妓才进入了历史记载。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=800",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=800"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_5280-5419",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5280-5419",
      "markText": "“娼妓业是充满艰辛的、道德上难以定论的许多选择中的一种。”在某些情形中，它为妇女提供了有限的控制权。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5280&rangeEnd=5419",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5280&rangeEnd=5419"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_6_14357-14402",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14357-14402",
      "markText": "也许改革的故事中需要一个坏蛋，而斥责鸨母比斥责嫖客容易些，因为后者中有许多上海的上层人士。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14357&rangeEnd=14402",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14357&rangeEnd=14402"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_6_18812-18885",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "18812-18885",
      "markText": "诸如此类的故事表明，一个“用人”在性行为和钱财方面所拥有的自主权，那种动摇了社会性别等级和阶级等级的定位，使得观察高等妓院景致的男人感到深深不安。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=18812&rangeEnd=18885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=18812&rangeEnd=18885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_5595-5624",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5595-5624",
      "markText": "她们讨价还价，她们既可能受到男人的凌辱，却也可能搜刮嫖客。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5595&rangeEnd=5624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5595&rangeEnd=5624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_17204-17241",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "17204-17241",
      "markText": "我始终不忘“事实”并不是被发现的，而是在人们生产意义的过程中被建构出来的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17204&rangeEnd=17241",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17204&rangeEnd=17241"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_30817-30913",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "30817-30913",
      "markText": "弘扬中华文化习俗成了对这问题的部分回应（此时中华文化习俗已被视为特殊的习俗，而不再具有普适性），所要弘扬的内容就包括翔实地阐述高等妓女精致高雅的社会交往习俗（所谓“西方有娼妓，我们则有名妓”）",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300056959&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30817&rangeEnd=30913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5cd32c90813ab7cbfg0193f0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30817&rangeEnd=30913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300056959_4_35463-35543",
